  <!-- EN: Relations with {0} have warmed. They now consider you neutral and will no longer attack you.\n\nThis happened because goodwill ({1}) has risen past {2}. If goodwill falls below {3}, {0} will become hostile again. If goodwill rises above {4}, they will become your ally and fight for you. -->
