  <!-- EN: Relations with {0} have become very close. They now consider you an ally.\n\nAllies will sometimes arrive to help fight your enemies when you are under attack. You can also call them for help at any time, at a cost of goodwill.\n\nYou've become allies because your goodwill ({1}) has risen past {2}. If goodwill falls below {3}, relations will return to neutral. -->
